{"tid":1550982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇諗過R下外國記者吹水","createTime":"2019-09-07T19:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:03:41.000Z","uid":54564,"like":113,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e21542850a091d3a37d786c9244fafde6282ad4a","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:28:29.000Z","msg":"自8月起都<span style=\"color: red;\">越嚟越多外國記者</span>到香港<br />\n<br />\n雖然話有留意開香港嘅記者會知香港發生緊乜事<br />\n但係有d初來報到嘅外媒其實可能會跟唔切香港嘅事<br />\n<br />\n尤其近日發生咁多事<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">日日新鮮日日甘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n就算普通香港人 唔係mon住tg/lihkg 都follow up唔切<br />\n更何況<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋唔識廣東話更加唔知發生緊咩事</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算佢拍完大家圍狗屋 上香獻花 屌狗<br />\n都唔明大家做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n例如今日喺mk 有成班防暴喺我哋跑過 <br />\n後面一堆街坊跟住班防暴圍屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實呢件事對外國人嚟講應該都幾震撼 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又話香港警察亞洲第一？</span><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>「點解香港市民要追住理應守護佢哋 自稱&rdquo;professional &ldquo; 嘅警察嚟屌呢？」</strong></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見d外媒都有跟住一齊跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢哋個樣<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好似好迷惘咁</span></strong></span><br />\n所以我鼓起勇氣咗勇氣用好惡劣嘅英文佢同佢解釋下現場做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n (請大家唔好笑我英文廢, 當時我甚至冇咁通順講到口疾疾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><em>當時大家嗌緊「黑社會」 popo話大家「嗌緊同一口號有同一訴求=構成非法集結」</em></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The police is saying that because we are shouting the same slogan, and we have the same demand, so they claimed that we are joining a illegal assembly&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;and we are shouting &lsquo;gansters&rsquo; as HK police did a lot of things to hurt HK people&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n講完之後佢哋先 「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」嘅樣 <br />\n先知道大家做緊乜 <br />\n然後有幾個外國記者都<em><strong>圍咗過嚟想同我傾計</strong></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但好快又有批防暴定蓄龍衝過嚟我淆底走咗佬所以冇同佢哋傾落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家成日話要<span style=\"color: red;\">爭取外國支持</span><br />\n除咗twitter + 登報 <br />\n我覺得簡單同佢哋講下<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>現場發生緊乜事</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>翻譯下現場人士嗌緊乜/ popo嗌緊乜</span></strong></span>比佢哋知<br />\n<br />\n<ins><em>等佢哋了解咗現場情況後 返去再自己落筆<br />\n寫返佢哋所見所聞出嚟 會係簡單得嚟又有用嘅做法</em></ins><br />\n<br />\n因為有時啲<span style=\"color: red;\">外國媒體唔知我哋到底做緊乜嘢</span><br />\n(有時候就算冷氣軍師都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<strong><em>點解要圍太子狗屋圍足成個星期？ -&gt; 因為要佢交代831</em></strong><br />\n講清楚好過d外媒以為大家純粹搞破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上呢份工作其實唔難做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">能夠簡單英文對答就已經好足夠</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我深信好多外國媒體都好希望知道大家廣東話講緊乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信用英文對答一定難唔到連登仔<br />\n只要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>比d勇氣一定做到</strong></span> (佢哋絕對唔會笑你英文差)<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 不過我覺得最好都係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如實翻譯/反映現場情況 </span></span></strong>唔好過分偏頗 否則佢自己了解完會覺得你講大話就唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家加入香城online全新職業 <span style=\"color: orange;\">「翻譯師」？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c750d62fd98a04a1fffcb845fc4e1eb28e2336","tid":1550982,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:28:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36ccc8dcf8b67e12718218bfbf044aec709bd54d","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:29:07.000Z","msg":"908 遮打見"},{"pid":"bbb3185b61352c1206cd5894aebe6974da8408b4","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:29:22.000Z","msg":"908 美領見"},{"pid":"ac3d19af34782e3311328fc2afd7ed987836441e","tid":1550982,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18b607db7c462493cf718c6a0c0c0bbe3edc462","tid":1550982,"uid":244230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa0a9ef93c803408f7599f622524db04f212c5c","tid":1550982,"uid":259842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbfc27c5bf10e77a97e48b14e138373e700c80e","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:34:50.000Z","msg":"甚至簡單d講下示威者<br />\n<br />\n點解向前<br />\n點解後退<br />\n<br />\n整rb有咩用 （今日都有對韓國情侶用英文問我做乜封住d巴士 -&gt; 驚狗包圍落車拉人） <br />\n<br />\n721唔見人 831打死人係咩意思<br />\n企疏d 又有咩用<br />\n<br />\n呢d都可以幫佢哋d唔識廣東話嘅外媒更有代入感 <br />\n大家喺度做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6fab05f1427d2c112e8eef87da2b0946cdedbf","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:37:13.000Z","msg":"或者有d外國人/中東人/南亞人其實唔知點解唔好影大頭<br />\n<br />\n用廣東話屌鳩佢佢根本都唔明<br />\n<br />\n倒不如一句 (利申英文好廢)<br />\n<br />\nYou can filming or take photo, but please not focus on our face<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bc1c97e920460486d21ccdae9373bb06f6b799","tid":1550982,"uid":263152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:37:53.000Z","msg":"推，好重要！"},{"pid":"36a9685f49d784bce6493d5e827544bb67e0cdb8","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d6fab05f1427d2c112e8eef87da2b0946cdedbf","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:37:13.000Z","msg":"或者有d外國人/中東人/南亞人其實唔知點解唔好影大頭<br />\n<br />\n用廣東話屌鳩佢佢根本都唔明<br />\n<br />\n倒不如一句 (利申英文好廢)<br />\n<br />\nYou can filming or take photo, but please not focus on our face<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:42:22.000Z","msg":"You can take video or photo but please do not focus on our face 好似好d？<br />\n<br />\n少壯不努力 老大徒傷悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199f88897fa7d966d0161b249403d7b56b965729","tid":1550982,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:44:07.000Z","msg":"推，好好嘅想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b7804cb2b40fdad2cffee3c3153dcdae4236ec","tid":1550982,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a178690d11c75850d467231e11de4ae938f227c","tid":1550982,"uid":51037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"a90f9774034ea2cbebdeb38e6adf03bd5fbd5a43","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:46:53.000Z","msg":"聽朝 美領見！"},{"pid":"2950152ce308f305e920fb5874fef1daaa0939cd","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:47:06.000Z","msg":"聽日 遮打見！"},{"pid":"a3b759a794e243b4ce2c7a0ccedde14c3669001c","tid":1550982,"uid":176840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:47:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"717d9732f784fcf10b6962ba58b1dc35ae5b8730","tid":1550982,"uid":176840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:48:07.000Z","msg":"認真嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b49ac6052ccfaf62c1ca7c4e7b34ca6ceeb8e8","tid":1550982,"uid":300387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:48:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"abab873294ba5e7c16ffc07f235e85d802c797ad","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:49:11.000Z","msg":"721 唔見人<br />\n831 打死人<br />\n<br />\n612 721 811 824 825 831 <br />\n908 大埔黑夜"},{"pid":"ffcf17b66b0dec1d11925cf1c1641b0b067f76f0","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:56:03.000Z","msg":"其實琴日已經想開post講<br />\n<br />\n見到HKFP 同一位 (懷疑身邊朋友831被打死)嘅女士做訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n位女士唔識英文 個肥仔又亂咁翻譯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得全能嘅香港人 + 連登仔女<br />\n真係需要企出嚟幫手同外媒溝通下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算係現場幫手同受訪者(有時入邨係c9多架嘛！)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做下翻譯都好幫到手"},{"pid":"f3b5d64a2d2c748e171bd8048a471c515627471d","tid":1550982,"uid":31655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48c271352b1d69edeeec8ad242919a74372d479","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:10:56.000Z","msg":"大家聽日遮打 美領見!"},{"pid":"66c65c9ea34c196a4d55664de54ced40a0555cd3","tid":1550982,"uid":13193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:12:46.000Z","msg":"TG @SuzanneSataline"},{"pid":"d761942e0749319c93355dfcf5dc31839d5abb03","tid":1550982,"uid":27804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T21:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a128f17c24e47ac14e1646eea419a24e3e493471","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:32:29.000Z","msg":"我今日跳咗閘 你又跳咗未"},{"pid":"f608ef2d7d6eff0d7ec68f96c359dc295470f151","tid":1550982,"uid":291689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9add42d566c51a129777694a1e184405af4cd51c","tid":1550982,"uid":267435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> but make sure you can give them reasons for every action we take because they always ask that"},{"pid":"0d62a1f6c1532c68f2150a0897b69c6bfa49b1fb","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"好多人"},{"pid":"3c921b990fd7c8713be2c5abedc15d79f4653602","tid":1550982,"uid":13774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fd45f7853edeb75c0c1fc4700291ec341f53ba","tid":1550982,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f18363727806a04174880274ccb8dbab0068e8","tid":1550982,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:45:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1d5d509f02212406809bcf46d0322d3ca3b0a23","tid":1550982,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e21542850a091d3a37d786c9244fafde6282ad4a","tid":1550982,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:28:29.000Z","msg":"自8月起都<span style=\"color: red;\">越嚟越多外國記者</span>到香港<br />\n<br />\n雖然話有留意開香港嘅記者會知香港發生緊乜事<br />\n但係有d初來報到嘅外媒其實可能會跟唔切香港嘅事<br />\n<br />\n尤其近日發生咁多事<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">日日新鮮日日甘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n就算普通香港人 唔係mon住tg/lihkg 都follow up唔切<br />\n更何況<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋唔識廣東話更加唔知發生緊咩事</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算佢拍完大家圍狗屋 上香獻花 屌狗<br />\n都唔明大家做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n例如今日喺mk 有成班防暴喺我哋跑過 <br />\n後面一堆街坊跟住班防暴圍屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實呢件事對外國人嚟講應該都幾震撼 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又話香港警察亞洲第一？</span><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>「點解香港市民要追住理應守護佢哋 自稱&rdquo;professional &ldquo; 嘅警察嚟屌呢？」</strong></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見d外媒都有跟住一齊跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢哋個樣<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好似好迷惘咁</span></strong></span><br />\n所以我鼓起勇氣咗勇氣用好惡劣嘅英文佢同佢解釋下現場做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n (請大家唔好笑我英文廢, 當時我甚至冇咁通順講到口疾疾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><em>當時大家嗌緊「黑社會」 popo話大家「嗌緊同一口號有同一訴求=構成非法集結」</em></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The police is saying that because we are shouting the same slogan, and we have the same demand, so they claimed that we are joining a illegal assembly&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;and we are shouting &lsquo;gansters&rsquo; as HK police did a lot of things to hurt HK people&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n講完之後佢哋先 「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」嘅樣 <br />\n先知道大家做緊乜 <br />\n然後有幾個外國記者都<em><strong>圍咗過嚟想同我傾計</strong></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但好快又有批防暴定蓄龍衝過嚟我淆底走咗佬所以冇同佢哋傾落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家成日話要<span style=\"color: red;\">爭取外國支持</span><br />\n除咗twitter + 登報 <br />\n我覺得簡單同佢哋講下<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>現場發生緊乜事</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>翻譯下現場人士嗌緊乜/ popo嗌緊乜</span></strong></span>比佢哋知<br />\n<br />\n<ins><em>等佢哋了解咗現場情況後 返去再自己落筆<br />\n寫返佢哋所見所聞出嚟 會係簡單得嚟又有用嘅做法</em></ins><br />\n<br />\n因為有時啲<span style=\"color: red;\">外國媒體唔知我哋到底做緊乜嘢</span><br />\n(有時候就算冷氣軍師都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<strong><em>點解要圍太子狗屋圍足成個星期？ -&gt; 因為要佢交代831</em></strong><br />\n講清楚好過d外媒以為大家純粹搞破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上呢份工作其實唔難做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">能夠簡單英文對答就已經好足夠</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我深信好多外國媒體都好希望知道大家廣東話講緊乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信用英文對答一定難唔到連登仔<br />\n只要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>比d勇氣一定做到</strong></span> (佢哋絕對唔會笑你英文差)<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 不過我覺得最好都係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如實翻譯/反映現場情況 </span></span></strong>唔好過分偏頗 否則佢自己了解完會覺得你講大話就唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家加入香城online全新職業 <span style=\"color: orange;\">「翻譯師」？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"422ba20ae41f287c444a5a5d528af05b324b9297","tid":1550982,"uid":42942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:48:15.000Z","msg":"推 支持"},{"pid":"831cb6cbb165e350de9b37f7f3dce95551da7491","tid":1550982,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:48:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d6ca6b28e905bc3e8e8a2ffa4884592e0d77d3e","tid":1550982,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bea0d2b9864fa4155e5c853e8e6c607097f687d","tid":1550982,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/